  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Logistics Supervisor",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Scope:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Maintain accurate inventory records in ERP system</li><li>Manage daily, weekly, and monthly stock counts</li><li>Monitor slow-moving, expired, damaged, or blocked stock and recommend actions</li><li>Lead, train, and supervise inventory control staff</li><li>Coordinate with operations and suppliers to ensure smooth inventory flow</li><li>Improve inventory SOPs and best practices</li><li>Identify ways to improve accuracy, reduce errors, and optimize warehouse space</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Diploma or above</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Excel</li><li>Minimum 5 years of experience in logistics, supply chain, or warehouse operations</li><li>Able to work under pressure and meet tight deadlines</li><li>Strong communication and leadership skills</li></ul><p><u><strong>Other Information:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Location: East/ Tuas</li><li>Timing: 8.30am - 5.30pm</li><li>Monday to Friday</li></ul><p>Interested candidates please kindly send CV to 89524450</p><p>Lee Mei Kiew Geraldine<br />CEI Reg: R1331173<br />Link2 Manpower Pte Ltd<br />EA License No: 22C1131</p>",
